	README

1. Install requred tools for parser
--------------------------------------------
You need to install bison and flex tools to do parser.

2. Config the directory of simics
------------------------
Modify "simics_dml_dir" variable in [dmlc.c:35] to your simics install directory.
Modify "dir" variable in [gdml.y:9] to your simics install directory.

3. Build the gdml
Run "make" to run

4. Run the gdml
./dmlc testcase/simple-device.dml

The C source file for Simics platform will be generated at output directory.
And also the grammar tree will output on your screen after run dmlc.

Thanks
SkyEye Team
